text: Samuel Parot (born 5 December 1964) is a Chilean equestrian. He competed in two events at the 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Chile Category:Equestrians at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2007 Pan American Games Category:Equestrians at the 2011 Pan American Games Category:Equestrians at the 2015 Pan American Games Category:People from Talca
